ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Manitoba Avian Influenza Assistance Initiative
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to help poultry and egg producers in Manitoba whose flocks were impacted following an outbreak of the avian influenza virus.
